  <Language_en_US>
    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_UNIVERSITYMUSEUM">
      <Text>University Museum</Text>
    </Row>
    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_BUILDINGS_UNIVERSITYMUSEUM_TEXT">
      <Text>A university is not just a hall of learning. Often, the most prestigious universities will collect artifacts to study, as well as display to the public in their own museum.</Text>
    </Row>
    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_UNIVERSITYMUSEUM_STRATEGY">
      <Text>The University Museum is a unique variant of the University. In addition to the University's normal benefits, the University Museum also contains 2 slots for Great Works or Art or Artifacts. The city must already have a Library in order to construct a University Museum.</Text>
    </Row>
    <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_UNIVERSITYMUSEUM_HELP">
      <Text>Adds +2 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science from Jungle tiles worked by this City. Allows Archaeologists to be built in this city.[NEWLINE]Contains 2 slots for Great Works or Art or Artifacts.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]City must have a Library.</Text>
    </Row>
	  <Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIVERSITYMUSEUM_THEMING_BONUS_HELP">
		  <Text>To maximize your bonus, make sure the Great Work Slots are all filled with Artifacts from different Eras, different Civilizations, and Civilizations other than you. The bonus increases with each criteria you meet.</Text>
	  </Row>
